Product Name: STAYFREE Dry Max All Nights XL - Sanitary Pads For Women, 2x42 pcs (Multipack)
Product Description: Stayfree All-night dry max sanitary pads for women for all-night protection. 2x better coverage, extra long and extra wide sanitary napkins for all-around protection throughout the night. These pads are suitable for regular to heavy flow. Dry max cover for best dry feel protection. Odour control system with natural oil that helps prevent foul odour and keeps you fresh. Individually packed pads so you can carry one with you always and stay prepared for any surprises. Ultra-Thin pads prevent leakages from all sides no matter how much you move in your sleep.
Manufacturer: Johnson & Johnson Pvt. Ltd. , L. B. S Marg, Mulund (West), Mumbai - 400080, India
Usage:
Unwrap the napkin. Remove the paper on the backside of the pad and place it on your panty.
Remove the release paper from the wings. Wrap the wings around both sides of the panty and press firmly. 
Before disposing of the pad in a dustbin, wrap it in the paper. 
Do not dispose of the pad in a toilet or flush it as it may clog.
